{"tid":651303,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意張衛健1996套西遊記","createTime":"2018-05-03T04:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T06:40:33.000Z","uid":161734,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8e3953f26df63221667248d1b3c705bf51637f62","tid":651303,"uid":161734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114156_4e54e0125827572300a0fe390c3d844f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114156_4e54e0125827572300a0fe390c3d844f.jpg&h=8f9a9933&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n講緊係大台第一集果套 無論劇情 設定 音樂 造形 選角 對白都係完美<br />\n唐三藏江華<br />\n張衛健孫悟空<br />\n黎耀祥豬八戒<br />\n麥包沙僧<br />\n<br />\n江華做到唐三藏果種為人師表嘅感覺 有時重有少少天然呆<br />\n張衛健演活咗孫悟空 唔再係乸型 做到果種調皮 前半部好cute 好似細路仔咁 後面就好man <br />\n黎耀祥隻豬八戒直頭無敵 同孫悟空果種化學作用真係笑到仆街<br />\n麥包做到沙僧果種戇直 呆下呆下咁 咩都要諗下 好似lag機咁<br />\n<br />\n呢套西遊記係最好睇 沒有之一 之後陳浩民做已經冇咁好睇 台灣果套齊天大聖孫悟空更加唔好講 只係搵一大堆明星撐場<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OoeY2b4iho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3OoeY2b4iho&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BSzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a784d294\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3OoeY2b4iho</a><br />\n精華重溫 無論主題曲定插曲都係完美 令人好放鬆<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjL5snZqLAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxjL5snZqLAE&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BSzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a594a668\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjL5snZqLAE</a><br />\n喂 你係豬黎架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果大台重播/重拍呢套放係黃金時間 我相信破60點都唔太難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">00後知唔知有呢套神作</span></span>"},{"pid":"dd2f921235a23473b771f5cd421a8bc60592bb77","tid":651303,"uid":94662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:09:59.000Z","msg":"首主題曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c116c8c086650267a892bd5c8a26f67d5dd1a044","tid":651303,"uid":83328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"重點係郭占美旁述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9303f108ff8337d9976c24e70221283da8c7c5","tid":651303,"uid":15481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"但我最怕我最怕師父失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a20876bf1ced12b3cf2ab3bf3b940ede4ee438","tid":651303,"uid":180173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:17:02.000Z","msg":"呢套我都好鐘意，四師徒選角真係無敵，之後陳浩民個可集真係食屎。"},{"pid":"1310d0e9c27683f502c8c615f9d062e4a081f075","tid":651303,"uid":39403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登班00後撚有睇過咩<br />\n講起張偉健，佢地淨係識&rdquo;劈啪你個龍的洞&rdquo;嗰套垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659e608168a9d88d2d266d0d0a1c256984e2dce1","tid":651303,"uid":34942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1310d0e9c27683f502c8c615f9d062e4a081f075","tid":651303,"uid":39403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"連登班00後撚有睇過咩<br />\n講起張偉健，佢地淨係識&rdquo;劈啪你個龍的洞&rdquo;嗰套垃圾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"嗰套係幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12a972de6